						<p><hi rend="italic">Hero-stone in the temple of Siddhēśvara.</hi></p>						

						<p>A.D. 1252.</p>						

						<p>This damaged record is dated in <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1174, Paridhāvi, Vaiśākha ba • • • • •</hi> (the <hi rend="italic">tithi</hi> and week-day are lost), corresponding to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1252, April-May.</hi></p>						

						<p>It mentions a <hi rend="bold">Jaitugi.</hi> The characters are Nāgarī and the language is Marāṭhi.</p>						

